  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Oxfam Novib - Fair Pension Guide Pilot</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Pension funds, participants</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the Fair Pension Guide is to initiate a race to the top among the most important Dutch pension funds in the Netherlands on corporate social responsibility (CSR). The Fair Pension Guide ise a joint initiative of PAX, Oxfam Novib, Amnesty International Netherlands, Friends of the Earth Netherlands and World Animal Protection. The Fair Pension Guide includes a web-based tool enabling pension savers to encourage their bank or insurer to be more socially responsible and sustainable by benchmarking them on fifteen themes and sectors. The Fair Pension Guide assesses pension funds&#x2019; policies on various social, economic and environmental issues such as climate change, human rights, labour rights, arms, transparency, for activities in sectors like oil/gas, fishery, etc. It engages pension savers via (social) media to put pressure on their pension fund for more sustainable investments and greater accountability. This project will likely expand to other countries over the coming years as part of the Fair Finance Guide International.</narrative>
  </description>
